author: ETA PRIME
description:
🚀 Thunderbolt 5 eGPUs Are Finally Here! In this video, we put the all-new Razer Core X V2 Thunderbolt 5 eGPUto the test and see just how much faster it really is compared to Thunderbolt 4.
I paired the Razer Core X V2 with the insane NVIDIA RTX 5090 GPU inside the ASUS ROG Strix 18 gaming laptopto push this enclosure to its limits. We also test Thunderbolt 5 performance with the MSI Claw A8 handheld over USB4 to find out how well next-gen eGPU technology works on smaller devices. #gaming #etaprime #thunderbolt5
